是的
Yeah.

547
01:08:13,880 --> 01:08:17,050
天被扯出了一个洞 太阳就下来了
Tore a hole in the sky, sun came down

548
01:08:18,210 --> 01:08:20,090
烧毁了一切
and burned everything.

549
01:08:20,550 --> 01:08:22,550
一切物 一切人
Everything and everybody.

550
01:08:23,180 --> 01:08:27,560
你很幸运 躲在了这种地方 或是地下
You were lucky to hole up and hide in a place like this or underground.

551
01:08:30,270 --> 01:08:32,310
但大多数人并不幸运
Most people weren't lucky.

552
01:08:35,520 --> 01:08:38,820
于是 一年之后 我们开始从躲藏的地方出来
So, a year later, we started coming out,

553
01:08:39,360 --> 01:08:40,570
人们四处游荡
and people wandered around.

554
01:08:40,650 --> 01:08:46,530
我不知道自己要做什么 我想找个方法活下去
I, not knowing what I was gonna do, trying to find a place to survive.

555
01:08:47,830 --> 01:08:50,540
一天 我听见一个声音
One day, I heard a voice.

556
01:08:51,870 --> 01:08:54,790
很难解释 但那就好像
It's hard to explain, but it was like it...

557
01:08:55,130 --> 01:08:57,750
就好像是从我内心发出的声音
Like it was coming from inside of me.

558
01:08:58,630 --> 01:09:02,880
但我能清楚地听到它 和我现在听你说话一样清楚
But I could hear it as clear as I can hear you talking to me now.

559
01:09:03,430 --> 01:09:05,390
那个声音怎么说？
What did this voice say?

560
01:09:05,930 --> 01:09:07,260
它指引我去了一个地方
It led me

561
01:09:08,180 --> 01:09:10,720
在那里我找到了这本书
to a place where I found the book

562
01:09:11,100 --> 01:09:13,270
它被埋在瓦砾之下
buried under some rubble.

563
01:09:17,230 --> 01:09:21,030
那个声音告诉我 把书带到西方去
The voice told me to carry the book out west.

564
01:09:22,490 --> 01:09:26,160
它告诉我 前方的路会成为我的指引
Told me that a path would be laid out for me,

565
01:09:26,240 --> 01:09:30,830
我会被指引到一个地方 使这本书安全的地方
that I'd be led to a place where the book was safe.

566
01:09:34,540 --> 01:09:36,750
它告诉我 我会被护佑
Told me that I'd be protected

567
01:09:38,130 --> 01:09:41,340
任何人任何事 都无法挡住我的去路
against anyone or anything that stood in my path.

568
01:09:44,510 --> 01:09:46,930
自那以后我就一直沿着指引前进
I've been walking ever since.

569
01:09:48,430 --> 01:09:52,270
你这么做 就因为脑袋里有一个声音让你这样？
And you did all that because a voice in your head told you to?

570
01:09:53,100 --> 01:09:54,430
是的
Yes, I did.

571
01:09:55,270 --> 01:09:57,060
我清楚当时我听到了什么
I know what I heard.

572
01:09:57,480 --> 01:09:59,230
我也清楚现在我所听到的
I know what I hear.

573
01:09:59,730 --> 01:10:01,570
我知道自己没疯
I know I'm not crazy.

574
01:10:02,280 --> 01:10:05,450
我也知道 没有它的护佑 我永远不会成功
And I know I would've never made it without help.

575
01:10:06,780 --> 01:10:09,320
- 那是什么？ - 这个问题不能回答
-What's that? -One question too many.

576
01:10:09,780 --> 01:10:12,910
睡觉吧 明天一早就要出发
Go to bed, we got an early start in the morning.

577
01:10:50,580 --> 01:11:04,800
嘿
嘿
Hey.

578
01:11:15,180 --> 01:11:16,930
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

579
01:11:17,310 --> 01:11:19,810
- 对不起 我以为你睡着了 - 我没睡着
-I'm sorry, I thought you were sleeping. -I wasn't sleeping.

580
01:11:19,900 --> 01:11:21,650
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

581
01:11:22,270 --> 01:11:23,820
我只想看一眼那本书
I just wanted to see the book.

582
01:11:23,900 --> 01:11:26,860
除了我没人能碰它 你明白吗？
Nobody touches it but me, you understand me?

583
01:11:27,530 --> 01:11:29,070
你懂我的意思吗？
Do you understand me?

584
01:11:29,160 --> 01:11:31,870
- 是的 我明白了 - 那就好 睡觉去
-Yes, I understand. -Good. Go to sleep.

585
01:11:41,830 --> 01:11:44,750
反正你也说了自己不识字 你看了也没用
You said you don't know how to read anyway. It's no use to you.

586
01:11:44,840 --> 01:11:45,920
是啊
Yeah.

587
01:11:46,970 --> 01:11:48,380
所以你教我看
So teach me.

588
01:12:08,610 --> 01:12:10,780
等等 等等 停下！
Hold up. Hold up! Stop!

589
01:12:16,620 --> 01:12:18,950
你说你已经走了３０年 对吧？
You know, you say you've been walking for 30 years, right?

590
01:12:19,040 --> 01:12:20,250
对
Right.

591
01:12:20,790 --> 01:12:22,370
你有没有想过自己可能是迷路了？
Have you ever thought that maybe you were lost?

592
01:12:22,460 --> 01:12:23,580
没有
Nope.

593
01:12:23,920 --> 01:12:26,000
可你怎么知道自己的方向是对的？
Well, how do you know that you're walking in the right direction?

594
01:12:26,090 --> 01:12:28,550
“我们靠信念走 不是视力”
"We walk by faith, not by sight."

595
01:12:29,590 --> 01:12:30,800
这是什么意思？
What does that mean?

596
01:12:30,880 --> 01:12:34,510
意思是你知道它是正确的 尽管还没有被证明
It means that you know something, even if you don't know something.

597
01:12:34,600 --> 01:12:35,680
这话根本说不通
That doesn't make any sense.

598
01:12:35,760 --> 01:12:37,720
不需要说通 这是信仰
Doesn't have to make sense, it's faith. It's faith.

599
01:12:37,810 --> 01:12:40,810
是黑暗平原上的光明之花
It's the flower of light in the field of darkness

600
01:12:40,890 --> 01:12:43,350
它给我前行的力量 你明白吗？
that's giving me the strength to carry on. You understand?

601
01:12:43,440 --> 01:12:44,690
那是你从书上看来的吗？
Is that from your book?

602
01:12:44,770 --> 01:12:48,730
不是 是约翰尼・卡什在福尔松监狱的演唱会
No, it's Johnny Cash live at Folsom Prison.

603
01:12:49,440 --> 01:12:50,530
什么？
What?

604
01:13:13,340 --> 01:13:16,510
- 你觉得那儿有人住吗？ - 不知道
-Do you think anyone lives there? -I don't know.

605
01:13:18,220 --> 01:13:19,970
或许会有水
Maybe there's water.

606
01:13:29,860 --> 01:13:31,400
呆在我身后 （标牌：禁止擅闯）
Stay behind me.

607
01:13:36,620 --> 01:13:38,120
这儿真奇怪
This is weird.

608
01:14:13,320 --> 01:14:14,690
你们是谁？
Who are you?

609
01:14:18,450 --> 01:14:21,200
我们只是旅者 我们无意伤人
We're travelers, that's all. Don't mean any harm.

610
01:14:21,290 --> 01:14:24,120
不得擅闯！你们没看到牌子吗？
No trespassing! Haven't you read the sign?

611
01:14:25,040 --> 01:14:27,460
我们很抱歉 我没看到牌子
We're very sorry. I didn't see it.

612
01:14:27,920 --> 01:14:29,130
你想干什么？
What's your business?

613
01:14:29,210 --> 01:14:30,290
- 我们只是 - 不想干什么！
-We were just... -No business!

614
01:14:30,380 --> 01:14:34,800
只是 我们很抱歉 如果您允许 我们这就离开
Just... We're very sorry, and if you let us, we'll be on our way.

615
01:14:35,510 --> 01:14:38,890
乔治 看看他们 其中一个只是个姑娘
George, look at them. One of them is just a girl.

616
01:14:38,970 --> 01:14:42,890
是啊 老生常谈 我听过不下百遍
Yeah. It's an old story, I've heard it a hundred times before.

617
01:14:43,020 --> 01:14:47,390
如今很少有人来拜访我们了 乔治对每个人都很多疑
We get so few visitors these days. George is suspicious of everybody.

618
01:14:47,730 --> 01:14:51,400
我叫玛莎 想喝点茶吗？
I'm Martha. Would you care for some tea?

619
01:15:02,160 --> 01:15:05,040
听听音乐？能让人放松的
How about some music? It's so soothing.

620
01:15:05,750 --> 01:15:06,960
乔治！
George!

621
01:15:26,930 --> 01:15:30,440
觉得怎样？很好听吧 请喝
How do you like it? It's nice. Please.

622
01:15:41,070 --> 01:15:45,120
- 好喝吗？ - 好喝 好喝 真是 味道很浓
-Is that good? -Good, good. That's... Taste is rich.

623
01:15:49,960 --> 01:15:53,540
你们单靠自己能活到现在真是不易
It's amazing that you two have survived out here all by yourselves.

624
01:15:53,630 --> 01:15:56,880
是这样的 乔治是个能工巧匠
Well, now, George is something of a handyman.

625
01:15:59,300 --> 01:16:02,550
他在这地方设了很多机关 好让这里更安全
He did a lot of work on this place, making it safe.

626
01:16:02,760 --> 01:16:05,260
我们可能老了 但很顽强
We may be old, but we're resilient.

627
01:16:05,930 --> 01:16:08,930
我们知道好些想霸占这里的人
We've known more than a few who've tried to take this place from us.

628
01:16:09,020 --> 01:16:11,190
- 是吧 乔治？ - 是啊
-Haven't we, George? -Yes, we have.

629
01:16:11,270 --> 01:16:13,900
- 是啊 - 我给你们看点东西 来吧
-Right. -I wanna show you something. Come on.

630
01:16:13,980 --> 01:16:16,230
乔治 不！不是现在！
George, no! Not now!

631
01:16:17,240 --> 01:16:18,490
来吧！
Come on!

632
01:16:21,240 --> 01:16:23,370
- 这些是 - 坟墓？当然
-Are these... -Graves? Sure.

633
01:16:23,660 --> 01:16:25,830
不把他们埋起来是很不文明的
Be uncivilized not to bury them.

634
01:16:25,910 --> 01:16:28,330
再说了 埋起来对土质也好
Besides, it's good for the soil.

635
01:16:29,290 --> 01:16:32,790
回到屋里来吧 我想我可以给你们做点三明治
Come on back inside. I think I might be able to rustle you up some sandwiches.

636
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:35,170
好 谢谢 非常感谢
Well, thank you, thank you very much.

637
01:16:35,250 --> 01:16:36,800
- 我们该走了 - 他们杀了那些人
-We gotta go now. -They killed all these people.

638
01:16:36,880 --> 01:16:38,460
不只是杀了 他们吃了那些人
They didn't just kill them, they ate them.

639
01:16:38,550 --> 01:16:41,470
- 她的手 她的手在抖 - 人肉吃太多了 咱们走
-Her hands... Her hands were shaking. -Too much human meat. Let's go.

640
01:16:42,130 --> 01:16:44,840
我找到了些肉 我想你们应该饿了
I found some meat. I hope you're hungry.

641
01:16:45,010 --> 01:16:46,550
不 不 谢谢
Nope. No, thank you.

642
01:16:46,640 --> 01:16:49,430
那个 我们 我们该走了
Well, we... We gotta be going.

643
01:16:49,520 --> 01:16:51,730
- 这么快？ - 是啊 恐怕是的
-So soon? -Yeah, I'm afraid so.

644
01:16:51,810 --> 01:16:54,440
- 你确定你们不留下来吗？ - 我确定 非常确定
-Are you sure you won't stay? -I'm sure, I'm very sure.

645
01:16:54,520 --> 01:16:56,310
把枪放下
Put the gun down.

646
01:16:56,480 --> 01:16:58,280
索拉拉 你拿着这个 替我们开下门 谢谢
Solara, you take this. Open the door for us, please.

647
01:16:58,360 --> 01:17:00,490
- 索拉拉 说谢谢你们的茶 - 谢谢你们的茶
-Solara, say thank you for the tea. -Thank you for the tea.

648
01:17:00,570 --> 01:17:01,780
很谢谢你们的茶
Thank you so much for the tea.

649
01:17:09,620 --> 01:17:11,290
回屋里去
Go back inside.

650
01:17:15,250 --> 01:17:16,290
乔治 出什么事了？
George, what's wrong?

651
01:17:16,380 --> 01:17:18,800
一大帮全副武装的恶徒 就是这么回事！
Whole company of armed degenerates, that's what's wrong!

652
01:17:18,880 --> 01:17:20,420
是他们把那帮人引来的
And they led them straight to us.

653
01:17:20,760 --> 01:17:23,840
- 我刚摆出些好瓷器 - 去你的瓷器吧！
-I just set out the good china. -Fuck the china!

654
01:17:23,930 --> 01:17:25,140
你还有其他武器吗？
Have you got any more weapons?

655
01:17:25,220 --> 01:17:27,930
武器？我给你看看武器
Weapons? I'll show you some weapons.

656
01:17:31,350 --> 01:17:33,690
- 你会开枪吗？ - 当然
-Can you shoot a gun? -Of course.

657
01:17:35,020 --> 01:17:36,860
快来！快！
Come on, come on!

658
01:17:37,060 --> 01:17:39,150
我们知道你们在里面
We know you're in there!

659
01:17:40,230 --> 01:17:42,860
到外面来 没有人会受伤
Come on out and nobody needs to get hurt!

660
01:17:47,620 --> 01:17:49,490
我会放你一马
I'll make it easy!

661
01:17:49,790 --> 01:17:52,580
把索拉拉和书交出来！
Send out Solara with the book!

662
01:17:53,000 --> 01:17:55,580
- 我们怎么办？ - 我知道自己在干什么！
-What are we gonna do? -I know what the fuck I'm doing!

663
01:17:55,670 --> 01:18:00,460
- 等等 - 我只要书和姑娘
-Wait, wait, wait. -That's all I want, the book and the girl!

664
01:18:02,260 --> 01:18:04,130
他们不打算出来
They ain't coming out.

665
01:18:29,910 --> 01:18:33,620
妈的！趴下！所有人都趴下！
Shit! Get down! Everybody, get down!

666
01:18:52,220 --> 01:18:54,770
嘿！那个你听到的声音
Hey! You know that voice you heard?

667
01:18:54,980 --> 01:18:56,810
有说过这件事情吗？
Did it say anything about this?

668
01:18:56,890 --> 01:18:59,310
我们会活着出去的 你我都是！
We'll get out alive, both of us!

669
01:18:59,480 --> 01:19:00,980
那我们呢？
What about us?

670
01:19:01,770 --> 01:19:03,530
没提到你们
Didn't mention you!

671
01:19:12,580 --> 01:19:16,200
停火！
停火！
Cease fire!

672
01:19:26,880 --> 01:19:28,880
玛莎？玛莎？
Martha? Martha?

673
01:19:28,970 --> 01:19:32,010
玛莎！玛莎！
Martha! Martha!

674
01:19:35,220 --> 01:19:38,270
- 玛莎 - 从侧面进去！
-Martha. -Go in on the side! Over on the side!

675
01:19:38,350 --> 01:19:39,810
你们这帮畜生！
You bastards!

676
01:19:40,560 --> 01:19:43,610
- 房子侧面！ - 你们这群畜生！
-The side of the house! -You fucking bastards!

677
01:19:48,950 --> 01:19:52,370
- 停火！ - 他们在干什么？
-Hold your fire! Hold your fire! -What are they doing?

678
01:19:52,450 --> 01:19:54,120
肯定不是什么好事
Nothing good.

679
01:21:08,070 --> 01:21:09,690
书在哪儿？
Where's the book?

680
01:21:16,620 --> 01:21:18,160
搜他的包
Check his pack.

681
01:21:36,800 --> 01:21:38,300
不在这儿
It ain't here.

682
01:21:41,100 --> 01:21:45,940
这是你最后的机会 交出书 不然我就把你埋在这儿
This is your last chance. You give it up or I swear I'll bury you out here.

683
01:21:56,820 --> 01:21:58,320
狗娘养的
Son of a bitch.

684
01:21:58,660 --> 01:22:00,450
咱们再试一次
Let's try this again.

685
01:22:05,170 --> 01:22:07,130
- 卡耐基！ - 什么？
-Carnegie! -What?

686
01:22:17,300 --> 01:22:20,810
好了 书在什么地方？
Now, where's the book?

687
01:22:26,020 --> 01:22:28,060
把书给他 求你了
Give him the book, please.

688
01:22:32,900 --> 01:22:34,530
别告诉他
Don't tell him.

689
01:22:43,540 --> 01:22:46,790
在房子里 电视机后面
It's in the house, back of the TV.

690
01:22:49,000 --> 01:22:50,590
去检查电视机！
Go check the TV!

691
01:22:51,210 --> 01:22:52,500
检查什么？
The what?

692
01:22:52,960 --> 01:22:56,670
你他妈气死我了 你 你去！去！
You're fucking shitting me. You, go! Go!

693
01:23:33,050 --> 01:23:36,260
无论什么 只要信 就必得到
Ask, and you shall receive.

694
01:23:41,760 --> 01:23:43,640
神是善的 不是吗？
God is good, is he not?

695
01:23:45,180 --> 01:23:46,640
一直都是
All the time.

696
01:23:49,020 --> 01:23:50,650
不是一直
Not all the time.

697
01:24:17,010 --> 01:24:18,920
不！不！
No! No!

698
01:25:04,510 --> 01:25:05,760
看到了吗？
You see?

699
01:25:08,020 --> 01:25:09,680
我怎么告诉你们的？
What did I tell you?

700
01:25:15,690 --> 01:25:17,320
他只是个凡人
He's just a man.

701
01:25:21,200 --> 01:25:23,820
不！别碰他！
No! Leave him alone!

702
01:25:24,530 --> 01:25:26,120
求你了！住手！
Please, stop!

703
01:25:32,710 --> 01:25:34,830
你的护佑呢？
Where's your protection now?

704
01:25:49,890 --> 01:25:51,310
为我祈祷
Pray for me.

705
01:25:54,810 --> 01:25:55,900
好吗？
Okay?

706
01:26:00,650 --> 01:26:02,030
我是认真的
I mean it.

707
01:27:20,230 --> 01:27:21,310
不！
No!

708
01:27:29,200 --> 01:27:30,490
妈的！
Shit!

709
01:27:31,990 --> 01:27:33,410
回去！
Go back!

710
01:28:17,200 --> 01:28:19,040
快点！快点
Come on! Come on!

711
01:29:18,600 --> 01:29:22,690
我们的油只够回去的 你要去追她吗？
We barely got enough fuel to make it back. You wanna go after her?

712
01:29:24,100 --> 01:29:25,150
不去
No.

713
01:30:46,390 --> 01:30:50,900
- 你去哪儿？ - 我要去西方 必须要去西方
-Where are you going? -I'm going west. Gotta go west.

714
01:30:53,610 --> 01:30:54,690
嘿！
Hey!

715
01:31:01,910 --> 01:31:03,040
给
Here.

716
01:31:20,220 --> 01:31:21,550
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

717
01:31:22,100 --> 01:31:23,560
为什么？
For what?

718
01:31:24,180 --> 01:31:26,480
- 都是我的错 - 不 不是你的错
-This. This is all my fault. -No, it's not.

719
01:31:26,560 --> 01:31:30,810
就是我的错 我要是没跟着你 这一切都不会发生
No, it is. If I didn't come with you, none of this would've happened.

720
01:31:31,650 --> 01:31:33,400
不是你的错
It's not your fault.

721
01:31:36,070 --> 01:31:37,820
我做了自己必须做的
I did what I had to do.

722
01:31:37,900 --> 01:31:41,370
我认为 任何事情都不能让你放弃那本书
I didn't think anything could make you give up that book.

723
01:31:41,450 --> 01:31:43,910
我以为它很重要
I thought it was too important.

724
01:31:46,500 --> 01:31:50,580
这些年我带着它 每天都读它
All the years I've been carrying it and reading it every day.

725
01:31:52,420 --> 01:31:55,340
我太着眼于保护它的安全
I got so caught up with keeping it safe,

726
01:31:55,420 --> 01:31:59,720
却忘记了按照从中学到的去生活
I forgot to live by what I learned from it.

727
01:32:00,840 --> 01:32:02,760
好吧 那是什么呢？
Yeah, and what's that?

728
01:32:03,760 --> 01:32:04,930
只是
Just...

729
01:32:08,270 --> 01:32:11,400
奉献他人 多过关照自己
Do for others more than you do for yourself.

730
01:32:13,690 --> 01:32:16,320
不管怎么说 这就是我从中学到的
That's what I got from it, anyway.

731
01:33:02,910 --> 01:33:04,450
你闻到什么了没有？
You smell that?

732
01:33:05,490 --> 01:33:07,330
- 什么？ - 在空气里
-What? -In the air?

733
01:33:07,450 --> 01:33:08,660
盐？
Salt?

734
01:33:13,380 --> 01:33:15,880
我们正在靠近海洋
We're getting close to the ocean.

735
01:34:14,890 --> 01:34:19,770
就是这儿了
就是这儿了
That's it.

736
01:34:52,850 --> 01:34:54,480
去找工程师！
Get the Engineer!

737
01:36:26,570 --> 01:36:28,240
别再靠近！
That's far enough!

738
01:36:29,530 --> 01:36:31,610
你们来这儿干什么？
What's your business here?

739
01:36:33,120 --> 01:36:34,660
我的名字叫艾利
My name is Eli!

740
01:36:35,540 --> 01:36:38,410
我有一本英王钦定本圣经
I have a King James Bible in my possession.

741
01:36:38,500 --> 01:36:40,000
呆在那里别动！
Remain where you are!

742
01:36:40,080 --> 01:36:44,170
别试图有什么动作 否则就开枪！
Don't attempt to make any sudden moves, or you will be fired upon!

743
01:37:01,060 --> 01:37:04,440
小心点 小心
Be careful with it. Be careful.

744
01:37:11,240 --> 01:37:12,860
小心点
Careful with it.

745
01:37:22,960 --> 01:37:24,460
他们没有武器
They're clean.

746
01:37:25,750 --> 01:37:28,590
我们做这件事已经很久了
We've been doing this for a long time now.

747
01:37:30,760 --> 01:37:34,090
- 感觉像是博物馆 - 不 可不只是博物馆
-Feels like a museum. -No, it's much more than that.

748
01:37:34,550 --> 01:37:37,350
这是我们将重新开始的地方
This is where we're going to start again.

749
01:37:38,060 --> 01:37:41,850
我们有一台印刷机 很快就可以投入使用
We've got a printing press. It'll be operational quite soon.

750
01:37:41,940 --> 01:37:45,350
我们要让人们了解那失落的世界
We're going to teach people about the world they lost.

751
01:37:45,440 --> 01:37:47,650
帮助他们开始重建
Help them start to rebuild it.

752
01:37:47,730 --> 01:37:52,150
我是说 看吧 莎士比亚 大英百科全书 只差几卷不全
I mean, look. Shakespeare. Britannica, missing only a few volumes.

753
01:37:52,400 --> 01:37:56,160
有一整个系列的 美妙的莫扎特和瓦格纳唱片
There's a whole series of beautiful Mozart and Wagner records

754
01:37:56,240 --> 01:37:58,490
依旧完好如初
in still very pristine condition.

755
01:37:58,580 --> 01:38:01,290
但从来没有圣经 至少目前为止没有
But never a Bible. Well, not until now.

756
01:38:02,210 --> 01:38:05,120
那么 我能问问它是什么样子吗？
Well, may I ask what condition it's in?

757
01:38:06,830 --> 01:38:08,290
很旧了
It's beat up,

758
01:38:09,250 --> 01:38:11,130
不过还可以用
but it will do the job.

759
01:38:11,970 --> 01:38:14,880
- 你觉得我能看看它吗？ - 是的 可以
-Do you think I could see it? -Yes, you may.

760
01:38:22,730 --> 01:38:25,140
- 好了 打开了 - 你打开了！
-That's it. It's open. -You there?

761
01:38:59,760 --> 01:39:01,310
你有什么东西可以写字吗？
Do you have anything to write on?

762
01:39:01,390 --> 01:39:04,350
能请你给我们那些书写纸吗？
Could you get us some writing paper, please?

763
01:39:05,020 --> 01:39:06,600
要很多
And a lot of it.

764
01:39:08,150 --> 01:39:09,810
很多很多
A whole lot of it.

765
01:39:10,860 --> 01:39:12,230
不可能
It can't be.

766
01:39:13,860 --> 01:39:14,860
不可能
It...

767
01:39:19,990 --> 01:39:21,580
不可能！
It's impossible!

768
01:39:23,290 --> 01:39:24,700
不可能！
It can't be!

769
01:39:27,870 --> 01:39:31,380
集中精神 写下来
Pay close attention and write down

770
01:39:33,170 --> 01:39:34,880
我说的每一句话
everything I say

771
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:39,010
每一个字
exactly as I say it.

772
01:39:43,680 --> 01:39:45,770
摩西之书的第一部
"The first book of Moses.

773
01:39:48,900 --> 01:39:50,520
叫做创世纪
"Called Genesis.

774
01:39:51,270 --> 01:39:54,440
第一章 第一节
"Chapter one, verse one.

775
01:39:58,360 --> 01:40:00,110
起初
"In the beginning,

776
01:40:01,410 --> 01:40:03,370
神创造天地
"God created the heavens

777
01:40:05,500 --> 01:40:07,080
"and the earth.

778
01:40:11,000 --> 01:40:12,330
第二节
"Verse two.

779
01:40:14,750 --> 01:40:18,720
地是空虚混沌
"And the earth was without form

780
01:40:21,840 --> 01:40:23,180
"and void.

781
01:40:28,020 --> 01:40:29,560
渊面黑暗
"And darkness

782
01:40:31,730 --> 01:40:34,650
"was upon the face of the deep.

783
01:40:38,320 --> 01:40:40,400
神的灵
"And the Spirit of God

784
01:40:42,450 --> 01:40:43,910
"was hovering

785
01:40:46,790 --> 01:40:49,000
"over the face of the waters.

786
01:40:52,830 --> 01:40:54,250
第三节
"Verse three.

787
01:40:57,960 --> 01:40:59,460
神说
"And God said,

788
01:41:03,720 --> 01:41:05,600
‘要有光’
"'Let there be light.'

789
01:41:10,770 --> 01:41:12,640
“就有了光”
"And there was light."

790
01:41:23,360 --> 01:41:24,990
索拉拉在哪里？
Where is Solara?

791
01:41:28,700 --> 01:41:30,040
在外面
Out there.

792
01:41:31,160 --> 01:41:32,500
她的选择
Her choice.

793
01:41:33,620 --> 01:41:37,420
我想带她回来 她拒绝
I tried to bring her back. She refused.

794
01:41:41,670 --> 01:41:44,090
她拒绝后 你对她做了什么？
What did you do when she refused?

795
01:41:50,480 --> 01:41:52,600
- 念出来 - 你对我女儿做了什么？
-Read it. -What did you do to my daughter?

796
01:41:52,690 --> 01:41:55,900
- 念出来！ - 你对我女儿做了什么？
-Read it! -What did you do to my daughter?

797
01:42:14,040 --> 01:42:16,080
你随时可以开始
You can start anytime.

798
01:42:24,590 --> 01:42:25,930
对不起
I'm sorry.

799
01:42:28,680 --> 01:42:31,220
太久了 我不记得了
It's been so long, I don't remember.

800
01:42:38,730 --> 01:42:41,570
- 你必须记得 - 必须？真的？
-You have to. -I have to? Really?

801
01:42:41,690 --> 01:42:44,240
不 不 你必须记得 求你了
No, no, no, no. You have to. Please.

802
01:42:47,910 --> 01:42:49,160
你的腿
Your leg.

803
01:42:50,540 --> 01:42:52,490
已经不疼了
It doesn't hurt anymore.

804
01:42:54,250 --> 01:42:55,750
我能闻到
I can smell it.

805
01:43:10,600 --> 01:43:13,010
你处心积虑要找那本书
You worked so hard for that book.

806
01:43:14,520 --> 01:43:17,270
你付出了那么多 那么多人的生命
You sacrificed so much, so many men.

807
01:43:19,730 --> 01:43:21,770
比你能承受的还多
More than you could spare.

808
01:43:23,780 --> 01:43:27,780
如今 那些从前连你的名字都不敢提的人
Now all those people who were too scared to even say your name,

809
01:43:27,950 --> 01:43:32,120
他们就在楼下 捣毁你的酒吧 你知道吗？
they're downstairs, tearing up the bar right now. Did you know that?

810
01:43:32,700 --> 01:43:35,330
而且没有人站出来阻止他们
And there's no one there to stop them.

811
01:43:36,660 --> 01:43:38,460
而你却如此狂热
And you're feverish.

812
01:43:41,540 --> 01:43:44,880
无法想象那种感觉 想要的东西近在咫尺
I can't imagine what it must feel like to have what you want so close

813
01:43:44,960 --> 01:43:48,630
- 却又似乎相隔天涯 - 住口！
-and it might as well be a million miles away. -Stop it!

814
01:43:52,180 --> 01:43:53,930
你要离开我吗？
Are you leaving me?

815
01:43:56,640 --> 01:44:01,690
克劳迪娅？
克劳迪娅？
Claudia?

816
01:44:05,150 --> 01:44:06,530
克劳迪娅！
Claudia!

817
01:44:33,640 --> 01:44:35,140
让开！
Get away! Get away!

818
01:44:35,220 --> 01:44:36,220
是我的！
It's mine!

819
01:45:55,340 --> 01:45:56,760
亲爱的主
Dear Lord,

820
01:45:57,390 --> 01:45:59,930
感谢你给我力量与信念
thank you for giving me the strength and the conviction

821
01:46:00,020 --> 01:46:02,810
好让我完成你交付给我的使命
to complete the task you entrusted to me.

822
01:46:27,380 --> 01:46:33,380
感谢你真诚的指引 让我克服道路上的诸多困难
Thank you for guiding me, straight and true, through the many obstacles in my path,

823
01:46:39,140 --> 01:46:42,680
感谢你赐予我坚毅 尽管周围的一切都已迷失
and for keeping me resolute when all around seemed lost.

824
01:46:43,600 --> 01:46:47,810
感谢你的保护 感谢你在道路上的诸多指引
Thank you for your protection and for your many signs along the way.

825
01:46:49,320 --> 01:46:53,900
我为一切我所行的善感谢你 对我所行的恶 我忏悔
Thank you for any good that I may have done. I'm so sorry about the bad.

826
01:46:55,950 --> 01:46:59,240
你不必离开的 你知道 我们很欢迎你留下
You don't have to leave, you know. You're very welcome to stay here.

827
01:46:59,330 --> 01:47:02,450
- 你会很安全 - 谢谢你
-You'll be perfectly safe. -Thank you,

828
01:47:03,750 --> 01:47:06,500
但这件事我必须做
but this is something that I have to do.

829
01:47:11,170 --> 01:47:12,840
你要去哪儿？
Where will you go?

830
01:47:14,130 --> 01:47:15,220
回家
Home.

831
01:47:21,390 --> 01:47:23,720
感谢你赐予我的朋友
Thank you for the friend I made.

832
01:47:23,930 --> 01:47:27,100
请保佑她 就像你曾经保佑我
Please watch over her as you've watched over me.

833
01:47:48,330 --> 01:47:51,380
感谢你最终让我安息
Thank you for finally allowing me to rest.

834
01:47:51,880 --> 01:47:53,800
我太累了
I'm so very tired,

835
01:47:54,510 --> 01:47:57,260
但现在 我将安息
but I go now to my rest, at peace,

836
01:47:58,340 --> 01:48:02,010
因为我知道 当我在世之时 我做的是对的
knowing that I have done right with my time on this earth.

837
01:48:11,020 --> 01:48:12,980
我打了场漂亮的仗
I fought the good fight.

838
01:48:13,820 --> 01:48:15,570
我完成了征程
I finished the race.

839
01:48:19,030 --> 01:48:20,660
我守护了信仰
I kept the faith.

840
01:39:51,510 --> 01:39:53,510
{\an8}盲文

841
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:52,650
建议戴上耳机

